I'll huff and I'll phish and I'll get your details;
your bank needs your password, your login, your tale.
By the hair of your chin-chin you click the link through;
and that's how the wolf got inside your inbox too.

Left at the fork and left again;
the wall is a wall but the path is plain.
It says keep going, it won't go back;
it circles the dead end till the batteries crack.
